That's actually really [00:52:30] true."

00:52:32.769 --> 00:52:35.029
Relationship is the key cornerstone.

00:52:35.029 --> 00:52:39.140
You have the four things that like people
should really think about in their life.

00:52:39.140 --> 00:52:40.480
Happiness is at the top.

00:52:40.480 --> 00:52:41.510
What are the other three?

00:52:41.510 --> 00:52:46.029
Eric: This is worked by Nash and Stevenson
at Harvard.

00:52:46.029 --> 00:52:52.609
They basically looked at the issue like the
work-life balance when people led fulfilling

00:52:52.609 --> 00:52:53.940
lives.

00:52:53.940 --> 00:52:56.869
What they found was that, again, that issue
of a collapsing metric, just having one number

00:52:56.869 --> 00:52:59.819
that didn't work because we all focus on money,
we forgot our relationships.

00:52:59.819 --> 00:53:02.299
We all [00:53:00] focus on relationships,
maybe you can't pay the rent.

00:53:02.299 --> 00:53:05.430
There is a balance here, so the collapsing
metric.

00:53:05.430 --> 00:53:10.990
The other mistake that people frequently make
is they try a sequencing strategy, which is,

00:53:10.990 --> 00:53:14.890
"First, I'm going to start out and I'm going
to do this job that I hate, but I'm going

00:53:14.890 --> 00:53:15.890
to make lots of money.

00:53:15.890 --> 00:53:19.549
Then, I'm going to focus on this and then
that's not going to work out, but then I'm

00:53:19.549 --> 00:53:24.069
finally going to ..." It's just life is not
that even because, obviously, it's relationships.

00:53:24.069 --> 00:53:26.730
You can't just start them when you're in phase
three.

00:53:26.730 --> 00:53:29.400
It needs regular consistent behavior.

00:53:29.400 --> 00:53:32.490
What they found [00:53:30] was that there
were actually four buckets that people needed

00:53:32.490 --> 00:53:35.039
to be regularly putting deposits in.

00:53:35.039 --> 00:53:38.829
The first was happiness, which is basically,
"Are you enjoying what you are doing?"

00:53:38.829 --> 00:53:39.829
The second one is achievement.

00:53:39.829 --> 00:53:40.829
Do you have goals?

00:53:40.829 --> 00:53:42.499
Are you getting closer to them?

00:53:42.499 --> 00:53:43.990
The third was significance.

00:53:43.990 --> 00:53:48.029
Is what you are doing is having an impact
